 <text id="A6068T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Enclosed secession badge made by author for recipient to wear.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Thomas M. Smiley</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     
      <pb n="1"  entity="Smiley38" pid="uva-lib:503205"/>
     
     <dateline>
      <date value="1862">[1862]</date>
     </dateline>
     <salute>Cousin Tom</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>I send you this Secession badge as a token or the regard I have for you. It is small but I
     wish you to wear it for my sake. I would be glad to <orig reg="receive">recieve</orig> a letter
     from you &amp; would most assuredly take pleasure in answering it.</p>

    <closer>
     <salute>Your friend &amp; Cousin</salute>
     <signed>Hannah M Berry</signed>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
